rows.label: tlk502111_msg0003
rows.name:
It's the first time I've seen
your face around here...

rows.label: tlk502111_msg0005
rows.name:
A Blade? I never saw a
Blade like you before...

rows.label: tlk502111_msg0006
rows.name:
You don't see much of the outside
world here in Luxuria, do you?

rows.label: tlk502111_msg0007
rows.name:
Are Superbian Blades really
different to Luxurian Blades then?

rows.label: tlk502111_msg0008
rows.name:
I mean, maybe one sort comes
into fashion, one goes out of
fashion, in different places?

rows.label: tlk502111_msg0009
rows.name: Hmmm... How can I explain it.

rows.label: tlk502111_msg0010
rows.name:
It's not like I thought, "I'll be this
or that sort of Blade". I just left it
to nature, I turned out like I did.

rows.label: tlk502111_msg0021
rows.name:
Hey, it was really nice
talking to you today.

rows.label: tlk502111_msg0022
rows.name:
Well, it was nice talking
to you too, ma'am.

rows.label: tlk502111_msg0023
rows.name:
Why, thank you. Here, why
don't you have this?

rows.label: tlk502111_msg0024
rows.name:
I had some time to kill, so I made these
for my grandkids. I got too much time
on my hands, so I made too many.

rows.label: tlk502111_msg0032
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Think ] Perhaps my charm failed me this time.
